OSCILLOFIGHT: POCKET RESONANCE
A Micro Boxing Pocket Game

COMPONENTS
- 1d6
- Pencil
- This sheet


FIGHTER SHEETS
------------------------------------------------------------
P1 BOXER
HP: 9     Drive: 0     Snap: 0
Stance: Idle / Jab / Cross / Hook / Shell

P2 BOXER
HP: 9     Drive: 0     Snap: 0
Stance: Idle / Jab / Cross / Hook / Shell


RING (1D LINE)
------------------------------------------------------------
P1 [■] ------------------------------ [■] P2

(Optional footwork: advance / retreat 1 step)


ENGINE CORE (Pocket Version)
------------------------------------------------------------
ROLL 1d6 → Apply Base Changes

ROLL   Drive   Snap
1      +0      -2
2      +0      -1
3      +0       0
4      +1       0
5      +2       0
6      +3       0

CARRY-OVER (Next Round)
- If Drive went up last round  → +1 Snap
- If Snap went down last round → +1 Drive

LIMITS
Drive stays between -4 and +4
Snap stays between -4 and +4


MOVES
------------------------------------------------------------
JAB
- Needs Drive ≥ 0
- Damage = 1 + Snap

CROSS
- Needs Drive ≥ 1
- Damage = 2 + Snap
- Costs 1 Drive

HOOK
- Needs Drive ≥ 2
- Damage = 3 + Snap
- Costs 2 Drive

SHELL (High Guard)
- Reduce incoming damage by (1 + Drive)
- Snap -1

IDLE
- No change


ROUND ORDER
------------------------------------------------------------
1. Both fighters pick stance (secret)
2. Roll 1d6
3. Apply Drive and Snap changes
4. Apply Carry-Over
5. Enforce Limits
6. Resolve stances simultaneously
7. Deal damage
8. Check for LIGHTS OUT


FINISH
------------------------------------------------------------
HP ≤ 0 → LIGHTS OUT (Opponent wins by TKO)


GLOSSARY
------------------------------------------------------------
Drive  = weight transfer / push behind the punch
Snap   = sting / whip / extension on the shot
Carry-Over = rebound after a big swing or drained flurry
Limits = you can’t load forever or go completely slack

JAB   = range finder / rhythm keeper
CROSS = power straight (costs Drive)
HOOK  = committed swing (high cost, high payoff)
SHELL = high guard, absorb shot, lose Snap
